  "texts": [
    "Future studies should aim to include participants from diverse educational contexts and investigate their interactions with the tutor bot.",
    "Future research efforts could involve a larger sample size and the incorporation of different types of tutor bots to enhance the validity of our findings.",
    "With the expectation of significant advancements in the capabilities of large language models (LLMs), we anticipate further research focused on training these models to effectively model students' understanding, improve dialogue management, and facilitate adaptive interactions.",
    "This research should also aim to develop strategies informed by learning sciences and pedagogy (see Fig. 5 below).",
    "Furthermore, students will not only be able to engage in one-on-one interactions with a personal chatbot but will also have opportunities to collaborate in learning with other students and chatbots."
  ],
